<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>

		<hr>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
				<div class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
							<div class="progress">
								<div 
									class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
									role="progressbar"
									aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
									aria-valuemax="100"
									style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
								></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>I have always had a passion for music which has given me a love for creativity and figuring out how things work. When I was younger one of my favorite T.V. shows was How itâ€™s Made. I love knowing how things work and appreciate the feeling of accomplishment that building, and making things work gives me.

				The first time I learned about coding was in high school. I took a few computer classes and enjoyed working in HTML and CSS. Two people influenced me to get into coding. My uncle (coder for about 10 years) and my brother (computer engeneering student).</p>   

				<p>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controler="jobHistory"
					>
						Job History
					</button>

					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#education"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controler="education"
					>
						Education
					</button>
				</p> 

				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							U.S. Postal Service (2 years)
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Hardware Essentials (1 year)
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Timpview High School
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Utah Valley University
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Bottega Tech
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

